	<h1 class="title">成龙说，他想和出狱后的儿子合作音乐跟电影</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
				<span class="name">美联社</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-08-06 08:13:00 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/13080/medium/13080.jpg?1438764483" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


